{"tid":87780,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【真‧勵志故事】IT女靠自己儲百萬首期 購柏傲灣劏房","createTime":"2017-01-20T06:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T08:10:45.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e76f663c8d569487cdb7a475f7f8d020cccc1d0c","tid":87780,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"【短片】【真‧勵志故事】IT女靠自己儲百萬首期 購柏傲灣劏房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbpvtaWEJT95wau5aja2kK1oVqdhpGsgPFkaNnVX6GctU?filename=3aq0DH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aq0DH2.jpg&h=f31a022e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增影片】從事IT，抽到50號前籌的柏傲灣買家甘小姐表示，成功以450萬元購入中高層318方呎開放式戶，靠自己儲了3、4年錢，沒有家人資助下付近百萬元首期入市，打算自住，不擔心樓價跌，即使跌，如果無賣就唔算蝕。<br />\n<br />\n她本身住於同區多年，一直都好想買此樓盤，之前抽過將軍澳海翩滙，但最終無入市，始終鍾情荃灣區，更表明同區其他新盤不及此樓盤，直言對周邊的長實（1113）項目無咩信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56197810&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56197810%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170120&d=GcW%2FYzJcQwdv7NKnLRP%2BTEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1b8af219\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56197810%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170120&h=86f1690d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56197810&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170120</a>  &quot;<br />\n<br />\n//邊個話IT狗冇用，呢位一定有實力，個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76543d26d8cc6eb837ce304bd90e83758e11d1f","tid":87780,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"咁既樣好難唔靠自己"},{"pid":"8954df6ee351c5ae203d7b42fb0aa22f1c068ad4","tid":87780,"uid":4418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-